This paper is about natural language processing and machine learning techniques for semantic parsing, which are typically covered in the arXiv sub-categories of cs.CL (Computation and Language) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The use of Sequence to Sequence models and Pointer Generator Network also suggests a focus on deep learning and neural networks, which are relevant to the sub-categories of cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Finally, the paper also mentions experiments and performance evaluation, which could fall under the sub-category of cs.SD (Software Engineering).
